Text.Value: ホワイトヘブンエリア２

Dialogue.Value: 目を見張るほどの立派な,電脳桜の大樹だ
[CALM WATER IS FAR MORE,SOOTHING THAN DIRTY OLD,TREES，RIGHT?]
[FILLED WITH POLLEN AND,INSECTS，ICK! I HEARD THEY,GROW IN DIRT!]
[THESE TREES ARE MORE,BEAUTIFUL THAN SOME,BORING WATER，RIGHT?]
[WHO EVEN DRINKS WATER?,AND WHAT DO FISH,EVEN DO IN THERE?]
[YOU HEAR THAT?!]
この桜の中に,過去にデリートされたすべての,データが詰まっているという
[I GAVE UP EVERYTHING,TO REACH UNRIVALLED,STRENGTH AND SKILL.]
[NONE MAY CLAIM TO SEEK,PERFECTION WITHOUT,SACRIFICING AS MUCH AS I.]
[I HAVE NO TIME FOR THOSE,WITHOUT DEDICATION.,BEGONE，AMATEUR.]
[I SEE YOU ALSO KNOW THE,PRICE OF TRUE POWER.]
[COME!,WE SHALL SEE WHO WILL,STAND AT THE PEAK!]
[DID YOU BRING YOURSELF,TO THE VERGE OF DEATH,JUST TO MOCK ME?]
[OR DO YOU TRULY BELIEVE,TO BE ABLE TO DEFEAT ME,IN SUCH A STATE?]
[IF YOU ARE SO CONFIDENT,IN YOUR SKILL，I WILL FREE,YOU OF YOUR DELUSIONS!]
[TO ALLOW VIRUSES TO,REDUCE YOU TO SUCH A,STATE....]
[I WILL BE MERCIFUL AND,ASSUME THAT YOU ARE,MERELY INCOMPETENT.]
[DO NOT SHOW YOURSELF,BEFORE ME IN SUCH A,PITIFUL STATE AGAIN.]
[UNBELIEVABLE....,TO BE DEFEATED AT THE,HEIGHT OF MY POWER....]
[HAVE I FINALLY BEHELD....,PERFECTION....?,AT LAST....]
[THANK YOU FOR SAVING,ME FROM THOSE AWFUL，,AWFUL NAVIS!]
[WELCOME TO HEAVEN,SQUARE! WE DON’T GET,MANY VISITORS!]
[I’M THE SPRITE THAT,CONNECTS LINK GATES!]
[I CAN LINK THIS SQUARE，,SUCH AS IT IS， TO YOUR,HOMEPAGE!]
[THE CONNECTION FEE IS,45000 ZENNY!]
[CREATE A LINK?]
[UNFORTUNATELY，YOU,DON’T HAVE ENOUGH,MONEY!]
[LINK CREATED!]
[I HOPE TO SEE YOU AGAIN,SOON!]
[NORMALLY THIS WHOLE,AREA IS A SAFE PLACE!]
[BUT SOMETHING HAS,DRIVEN ALL THE SPIRITS,INTO A FRENZY!]
[JUST WHAT IS THE ,CYBERWORLD COMING TO?]
